<section class="ulasim-container">
    <h2>Transportation Options to the Fairground</h2>

    <div class="ulasim-item">

        <div class="ulasim-content">
            <h3>Metrobus</h3>
            <p>The fastest way to get to the fairground from Zincirlikuyu, Mecidiyeköy and Avcılar is by
                Metrobus. You can use the 34 A metrobus line, transfer from the Atatürk - Şirinevler stop to the
                Atatürk Airport (M1A) metro, get off at the World Trade Center/Istanbul Fair Center station and
                reach the fairground.</p>
            <a href="http://www.iett.gov.tr" target="_blank">www.iett.gov.tr</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ulasim-item">

        <div class="ulasim-content">
            <h3>Metro</h3>
            <p>The Yenikapı-Ataturk Airport metro line (M1A) passes through the Istanbul World Trade
                Center/Istanbul Fair Center complex. Transfers can be made to the Ataturk Airport metro line
                from the Zeytinburnu or Şirinevler metrobus stops.</p>
            <a href="https://metro.istanbul" target="_blank">metro.istanbul</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ulasim-item">

        <div class="ulasim-content">
            <h3>Bus</h3>
            <p>You can reach Istanbul Fair Center by using HVİST-13 buses departing from Istanbul Airport and
                M1A Yenikapı-Atatürk Airport metro route from Ataköy-Şirinevler metro stop.</p>
            <a href="http://www.iett.gov.tr" target="_blank">www.iett.gov.tr</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ulasim-item">

        <div class="ulasim-content ms-5 ps-3">
            <h3>Car</h3>
            <p>You can reach the fairground by road from 3 alternative arteries (E5, TEM and Coastal Road).</p>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ulasim-item">

        <div class="ulasim-content">
            <h3>Marmaray</h3>
            <p>You can reach the fairground in 5 minutes by taxi at the Yeşilyurt stop using the Halkalı-Gebze
                Marmaray line.</p>
            <a href="https://marmaray.istanbul/" target="_blank">https://marmaray.istanbul/</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

